                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7761" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0209</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1602 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG赋能“智藻”：金山环保的太湖蓝藻治理之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG Empowering Intelligent Blue-Algae Treatment: The Journey of Jingshan Environmental Protection Company in Taihu Lake Blue-Algae Remediation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浦徐进，吴雪艳，张文，王秋寒</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏金山环保科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共关系/外事部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金山环保；ESG实践；太湖蓝藻治理；智慧化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jingshan Environmental Protection Company; ESG practice; Taihu Lake blue-algae remediation; intelligent transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为国内环保水处理和ESG实践的领军企业，金山环保早在2014年就参与江苏省太湖蓝藻治理工作。2019年，在全面在积累了多年蓝藻治理相关经验之后，金山环保对07年蓝藻危机以来江苏省太湖治理发展历程、以及企业相关实践，做了全方位的复盘，深入而详细分析了太湖蓝藻十多年治理过程中各方面存在的症结，并提出“ESG赋能‘智藻’”的新方案。随后，公司开启“金山—太湖蓝藻‘智理’示范区”的ESG实践项目建设，打响了金山环保谋求太湖蓝藻治理智慧化转型的“第一战”。本案例以“示范区”建设历程为线索，通过事件回顾、企业家采访、企业考察等方法，完整梳理了金山环保在推动太湖蓝藻治理智慧化转型过程中遭遇的环境(Environment)、社会(Social)和公司治理(Government)方面的挑战，以及应对措施，对环保企业ESG可持续发展实践具有现实的参考和借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a leading domestic environmental water treatment and ESG practice company, Jingshan Environmental Protection Company joined the Taihu Lake blue-algae remediation efforts as early as 2014. In 2019, after 5 years of experience in blue-algae treatment, Jingshan conducted a comprehensive review of the development of Taihu Lake treatment in Jiangsu Province since the 2007 blue-algae crisis, as well as related corporate practices. The Senior Management Team deeply and thoroughly analyzed the various issues that existed in the algae remediation process over the past decade and proposed a new plan of &quot;ESG Empowering &#39;Intelligent Blue-Algae&#39;.&quot; Subsequently, the company launched the &quot;Jingshan-Taihu Algae &#39;Intelligent Management&#39; Demonstration Zone&quot; project, marking the first battle of Jingshan Company&#39;s pursuit of intelligent transformation in Taihu Lake blue-algae treatment. This case study, based on the construction process of the &quot;Demonstration Zone,&quot; uses event reviews, entrepreneur interviews, and company inspections to comprehensively sort out the challenges encountered by Jingshan Company in promoting the intelligent transformation of Taihu Lake blue-algae treatment in terms of environment, social, and corporate governance (ESG), as well as ESG response measures. It has practical reference and significance for other environmental protection companies in their ESG sustainable development practices.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业伦理与社会责任》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
